{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We should have given it up anyway, because then we went into another room where we had to undress completely-- completely, with the exception of the shoes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we had to go into another room, where you had a lot of prisoners sitting on benches and you were shaved-- head, armpits, and your private parts, completely and totally shaved.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then you went through another room of people that were sitting in benches, and wiped your body where you were shaved with some kind of chemical that was burning your body like fire.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now when you saw from far away that you're going into the shower, you couldn't wait to get into the shower.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went, we showered, we walked through the other end, we got a striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The women didn't have striped uniforms yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were getting-- giving out clothes, because the barracks, the fences, you could see how the women were dressed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was-- in-- in-- in that transport, they still have the striped uniforms with striped hats-- no underwear, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no socks, just wooden shoes-- they called them Trippen-- wooden shoes, a striped uniform, and a striped hat.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not get a number because in 1944, in September and October, that was a lucky time to come in to Auschwitz, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the order that came from the high command in Germany to every camp-- don't kill people if they're able-bodied, because we need them now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the time when they started drafting people up to 65 years old, in boys, 12 years and up, to go into the landover's army, German landover's army, or to the other army.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
